reviewText: I bought this as a joke for my sister-in-law because we always sing the "She's My Sister" song from our childhood, but it was new characters that I didn't even knownot the characters we grew up with.  Not my favorite.
LOVE THE PRODUCT, IF I NEED ANOTHER ONE, AMAZON.COM IS WHERE I'M GOING TO GET IT.
